<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Reset Your Password - Aboda</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; } .header {
      background-color: #1b8057; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align:
      center; border-top-left-radius: 25px; border-top-right-radius: 25px; }
      .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; } .content { background-color:
      #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; padding: 20px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 25px; border-bottom-right-radius: 25px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #1b8057; color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top:
      20px; } .footer { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;
      color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <div class='logo'>Aboda</div>
    </div>
    <div class='content'>
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
      <p>Hello {{email}},</p>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset your password for your Aboda account. If
        you requested this change, please click the button below to reset your
        password:
      </p>
      <a href='{{reset_url}}' class='button'>Reset Password</a>
      <p>
        If you did not request to reset your password, you can safely ignore
        this email. Your password will remain the same.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class='footer'>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Aboda Corp. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href='{{privacyLink}}'>Privacy</a>
        |
        <a href='{{termsLink}}'>User Terms & Condition</a>
      </p>
      <p>Contact: aboda@gmail.com | +62861527498</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>